A fast tab vault and tab archive with search and easy import/export. This allows you to save, retrieve and organize tabs in a local database, and easily scales to 10,000s of tabs.

For extra convenience, there is also built-in incremental search, deduplication options and export.

Minimal but highly functional (~800 LoC), backed by IndexedDB for speed, and won't lose your data like other tab managers. No tracking is included, we respect your privacy. 

Information on contributing is on GitHub.
